con:testCase.con:description:
Basic tests for Flickr API - including both authenticated and anonymous resources: - First request makes sure the interestingness list always contains 100 entries (which it won't when a new day starts) - Send request makes sure the specified user can be found - Third request checks that "Nikon" is in the list of cameras - Fourth request checks that there are photos available for "Stockholm"
see http://www.flickr.com/services/api/
